BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:All\,\n\nPlease hold this time biweekly for a team meeting.  Pl
 ease plan to meet in person in the conference room\; a Teams link has been
  added in the event one of us is working remotely.\n\nA draft meeting outl
 ine is available [​docx icon]  here<https://myuva.sharepoint.com/:w:/r/s
 ites/UVABattenIntranet/Career%20Services/Team%20Meetings/2025-2026%20Team%
 20Meeting%20Agenda%20+%20Notes.docx?d=w360453f1835f4597bd7acfa80c53f846&cs
 f=1&web=1&e=D4x1c3>\; I’ll shift the content for future meetings above t
 he prior meeting details.  Please add content\, links\, or other informati
 on no later than COB the prior Tuesday.\n\nLooking forward to kicking off 
 this series and supporting one another towards a successful and impactful 
 year of growth for our team and those we serve\,\n\nSarah\n\n_____________
 ___________________________________________________________________\nMicro
 soft Teams Need help?<https://aka.ms/JoinTeamsMeeting?omkt=en-US>\nJoin th
 e meeting now<https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19%3ameeting_ZjEzZ
 Tg1MjktOWEzYS00NTUxLTk3NGEtOGUyMzBhMDhjYzVi%40thread.v2/0?context=%7b%22Ti
 d%22%3a%227b3480c7-3707-4873-8b77-e216733a65ac%22%2c%22Oid%22%3a%229e042f6
 3-e683-4138-8266-e729ce0fb655%22%7d>\nMeeting ID: 268 271 565 283\nPasscod
 e: su3F8jE2\n________________________________\nFor organizers: Meeting opt
 ions<https://teams.microsoft.com/meetingOptions/?organizerId=9e042f63-e683
 -4138-8266-e729ce0fb655&tenantId=7b3480c7-3707-4873-8b77-e216733a65ac&thre
 adId=19_meeting_ZjEzZTg1MjktOWEzYS00NTUxLTk3NGEtOGUyMzBhMDhjYzVi@thread.v2
 &messageId=0&language=en-US>\n____________________________________________
 ____________________________________\n
