DESCRIPTION:Draft Outline:\n[​docx icon] newsletter-August 2025.docx<http
 s://myuva-my.sharepoint.com/:w:/g/personal/cm2x_virginia_edu/EaoKn0SGpzZHi
 z_9lurzaIQBMEEFh3sMoy2eBC9kJUGvhA?e=PlXqjF>\n\nHi all –\nThis day/time w
