 review multiple things before the semester starts in earnest. Quick agenda
 :\n\n  *   First newsletter of Fall – send 8/21 or 8/28?\n  *   Identify
  contents for first issue\n  *   Set standing bi-weekly time slot for this
  group throughout semester\n  *   Quick review of status of Marcom work pl
 ans from summer planning sessions (more on that soon)\nThanks much!\n-Cat\
 n[https://st2.zoom.us/static/6.3.39695/image/new/ZoomLogo_110_25.png]<http
 s://zoom.com/>\nHi there\,\nCat McCue is inviting you to a scheduled Zoom 
 meeting.\nJoin Zoom Meeting<https://virginia.zoom.us/j/97422696543?pwd=jNq
 8TjmVYIAKhGaMRdx4ghMWoWa5XQ.1&from=addon>\nOne tap mobile:\nUS: +164655886
