 22696543#<tel:+16513728299\,\,97422696543>\nMeeting URL:\nhttps://virginia
 .zoom.us/j/97422696543?pwd=jNq8TjmVYIAKhGaMRdx4ghMWoWa5XQ.1&from=addon\nMe
 eting ID:\n974 2269 6543\nPasscode:\n568207\nJoin by Telephone\nFor higher
  quality\, dial a number based on your current location.\nDial:\n+1 646 55
 8 8656 US (New York)\n+1 651 372 8299 US (Minnesota)\n+1 786 635 1003 US (
 Miami)\n+1 267 831 0333 US (Philadelphia)\n+1 301 715 8592 US (Washington 
