BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Hi All\,\n\nAs of late yesterday\, we now have a Batten Hour sp
 eaker for Monday\, September 15th. His name is Paul Carrese\, and he will 
 be visiting from Arizona State University. This will serve as the Universi
 ty's Constitution Day event\, which means Major Events and the President's
  office will have some involvement. If at all possible\, I would love to c
 onnect with the group today to discuss this further and get some things or
 ganized before we head into the weekend. Apologies in advance for the same
  day request but this is going to be a big one.\n\nSetting location for Co
 nf. Room A\, but will leave the teams option on.\n\nSean Michael\, can we 
 go ahead and request UPD?\n\nKayla\, rather than pizza\, let's do boxed lu
 nches (wherever works best).\n\nMarketing and comms team\, let me work on 
 getting a headshot of him.\n\n____________________________________________
 ____________________________________\nMicrosoft Teams Need help?<https://a
 ka.ms/JoinTeamsMeeting?omkt=en-US>\nJoin the meeting now<https://teams.mic
 rosoft.com/l/meetup-join/19%3ameeting_MTMzODhhZjQtNTRkMC00ZjBmLTg3NjgtYTNh
 OWZjMGIzZjA1%40thread.v2/0?context=%7b%22Tid%22%3a%227b3480c7-3707-4873-8b
 77-e216733a65ac%22%2c%22Oid%22%3a%22d9b8668c-88c6-438a-a60a-255701732f19%2
 2%7d>\nMeeting ID: 215 040 782 034 1\nPasscode: om29iT9j\n________________
 ________________\nFor organizers: Meeting options<https://teams.microsoft.
 com/meetingOptions/?organizerId=d9b8668c-88c6-438a-a60a-255701732f19&tenan
 tId=7b3480c7-3707-4873-8b77-e216733a65ac&threadId=19_meeting_MTMzODhhZjQtN
 TRkMC00ZjBmLTg3NjgtYTNhOWZjMGIzZjA1@thread.v2&messageId=0&language=en-US>\
 n_________________________________________________________________________
 _______\n
